{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "夜深，萧少英与葛新来到第八重院子，会见假扮病人的李千山。李千山揭下人皮面具，露出真容。葛新回忆起当年想投入双环门被李千山拒绝的往事，萧少英曾暗中相助。葛新表示要杀人，但目标竟是萧少英。李千山与葛新坦白——他们皆是青龙会卧底，利用葛停香消灭双环门，再借萧少英之手除掉天香堂。青龙会布局深远，四位堂主之死、刺客、郭玉娘皆是棋子。萧少英突然祭出七星透骨针击杀葛新，并揭示自己早有防备——他给了葛新一筒假针筒用于栽赃王桐，自己则留了一手。李千山与萧少英在斗室中生死相搏，灯火倾倒在烈酒上引燃大火，将一切恩怨埋葬。第五种武器不是多情环，而是仇恨。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大厨房里每顿都要开三次饭，每次都要开十来桌。今天晚上，我每顿都加了菜。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "什么菜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "菜是普通的红烧肉，佐料却是特别为他们从辰州买回来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "什么佐料？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "瞌睡药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪他们都睡得这么熟。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们果然来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "你知道我们会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "你为什么还不走？是不是知道已无路可走了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "你脸上这张人皮面具做得并不好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以我总是不愿让人看见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "你想不到我会看出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "但我却知道你一定会猜出来的，我一直认为你是个绝顶聪明的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "我们已有两年不见了，想不到竟会在这种情况下再见。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "我也想不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "你若不怕酒里有毒，我也可以替你倒一杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "我怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "你记不记得我们是怎么认识的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "昔年我本来也想投入双环门，我被仇家追得很紧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "可是有个人坚持不答应，因为他已看出你是为了避祸而来的，他不愿惹麻烦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以我只好走了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "可是我却很同情你，所以你走了之后，我还追出很远，在暗中助你杀了三个从中原追来的仇人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以我们就交了朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "你还记不记得，那个坚持不让你入双环门的人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "李千山。现在你是不是想要我替你杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "他毕竟总算还是我的同门兄弟。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以你自己不愿出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "现在你已准备杀人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "只不过我要杀的人并不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "不是他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "我知道你一定想不通这是怎么回事的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "我们并不是好朋友，只不过他若要我杀人时，我就杀。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_ge_xin",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "因为一条龙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青龙……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你们都是青龙会的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "本属青龙会，来作卧底奸；九月初九日，翱翔上九天。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "他坚持不让我人双环门，只为他要我加入青龙会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "你早已人了青龙会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以葛停香要来勾引我，我当然不会不答应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "因为你正好乘机利用他，来消灭双环门。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "然后你再利用我，来消灭天香堂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以你要我写那三封信时，也正合我的心意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那些蒙面的刺客，也是你们找去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "所以天香堂的四位堂主都死了，双环门的七大弟子也死了三个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "我们特地留下杨麟和王锐，为的要引你上钩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭玉娘当然也是你们的人，所以她才会时常到这里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xin",
      "speaker_name": "葛新",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "葛成也是我们的人，所以他才替郭玉娘说谎的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你们却让我害死了郭玉娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "现在我们的任务已完成，双环门和天香堂，都已被我们连根除尽，她的死活，我们已不放在心上。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "想不到你居然还有一筒七星透骨针。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "莫忘七星透骨针留在世上的还有两对。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "你将一对给葛新，故意要他在背后暗算你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "那只不过是一出戏，特地演给葛停香看的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "然后你就要葛新乘机将针筒塞人王桐怀里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "我也学会了栽赃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李千山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "text": "现在你又用它杀了葛新。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "萧少英",
      "listener": "char_li_qian_shan",
      "text": "他也不知道我还有一对。无论做什么事，我总会为自己留一着的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
